Sentencas: A novel composition of BaCe0.7Ta0.1Y0.2O3-6 (BCTY10) electrolyte membrane was successfully fabricated on porous NiO-BCTY10 anode substrate.
Titulo: A novel anode supported BaCe0.7Ta0.1Y0.2O3-δ electrolyte membrane for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The anode was prepared through a route combining a solid state reaction and a wet chemical method.

Titulo: A novel anode supported BaCe0.7Ta0.1Y0.2O3-δ electrolyte membrane for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cell
